text: Ronnie Masterson (4 April 1926 - 10 February 2014) was an Irish actress. She was born in Dublin. She started acting in 1965. She also co-founded Old Quay Productions. Masterson died on 10 February 2014, aged 87. She was outlived by her four children with actor, Ray McAnally.
